text: G. Wallace "Wally" Caulk Jr. (born February 7, 1941) is an American politician. He was a Republican member of the Delaware House of Representatives, representing District 33 from 1985 until his retirement in 2006. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:People from Milford, Delaware Category:Members of the Delaware House of Representatives
title: G. Wallace Caulk Jr.
